rescale <- function(x, from, to) {
  maxx <- max(x)
  minx <- min(x)
  out <- (to - from) * (x - minx)
  out <- out / (maxx - minx)
  out + from
}

GC1<-data.frame(flow=GC1_LIM$Unknowns,
                mean=round(colMeans(GC1_xs$X),3),
                station="GC1")
GS1<-data.frame(flow=GS1_LIM$Unknowns,
                mean=round(colMeans(GS1_xs$X),3),
                station="GS1")
df<-rbind(GC1,GS1)
df$arrow=round(rescale(df$mean,1,15),2)
df
